<p>Last Updated: August 26, 2024

Welcome to Fictional Library! We value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your data when you use our library management system.

1. Information We Collect
Personal Information: We collect personal details such as your name, email address, phone number, and library card information when you register or update your account.
Borrowing History: Information about the books you borrow, return dates, and overdue fines.
Technical Data: Details about your device and browser, including IP address, browser type, and operating system.
2. How We Use Your Information
Library Services: To manage your account, process book checkouts and returns, and send reminders for due dates.
Improvement: To analyze usage patterns and enhance the functionality of our system.
Communication: To provide updates about library events, new arrivals, and other relevant information.
3. How We Protect Your Information
Security Measures: We use encryption, firewalls, and secure servers to protect your data.
Access Control: Only authorized personnel have access to your personal information, and we ensure they are trained in data protection practices.
4. Sharing Your Information
Service Providers: We may share information with third-party service providers who assist us in operating our library system, under strict confidentiality agreements.
Legal Obligations: We may disclose your information if required to comply with legal obligations or respond to lawful requests.
5. Your Rights
Access and Correction: You have the right to access and update your personal information. Please contact us to make changes.
Opt-Out: You may opt out of receiving promotional emails by following the unsubscribe link in our communications.
6. Changes to This Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. Any changes will be posted on our website, and we encourage you to review it regularly.

7. Contact Us
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or our data practices, please contact us:

Email: support@fictionallibrary.com
Phone: (123) 456-7890
Address: 123 Library Lane, Booktown, BK 12345
Thank you for being a part of Fictional Library!.</p>
